{"tid":1266762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會展兩展覽須提前結束 參展商估計損失達十萬","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T16:10:05.000Z","uid":41404,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9172c88d84f6f289359536cb435fe4828d94b6b3","tid":1266762,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"警方是日起在灣仔金紫荊廣場一帶加強佈防，包括放置多重巨型水馬陣，又禁止沒有許可證的車輛及人士接近金紫荊廣場，防範有人干擾七一升旗禮進行。<br />\n<br />\n基於保安理由，政府亦要求國慶酒會之舉行地點香港會議展覽中心明日關閉，原定於六月二十八至三十日在會展舉行的「優質寵物用品展」及「香港家居博覽」須提早於今晚結束。主辦單位對有關決定感到「非常無奈」，有參展商估算，有關安排將令其公司損失近十萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://tmhk.org/2019/06/29/金紫荊一帶加強保安-會展兩展覽須提前結束-參展商/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftmhk.org%2F2019%2F06%2F29%2F%E9%87%91%E7%B4%AB%E8%8D%8A%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89-%E6%9C%83%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A9%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD%E9%A0%88%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-%E5%8F%83%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJoxYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=e00f46b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tmhk.org/2019/06/29/金紫荊一帶加強保安-會展兩展覽須提前結束-參展商/</a>"},{"pid":"3ca4dd69379d80554eeb3bf734c6f252b276eda0","tid":1266762,"uid":49184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"文宣組又有新題材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209a40a8976ef6d41c6813b7f8de549d967e4677","tid":1266762,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:35:26.000Z","msg":"#又係佔中"},{"pid":"1b52ea717719ee3ef45b13604a358c54d3bef881","tid":1266762,"uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"你仲有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb959f9a66427cf53d41a0e78cb551ad997d426","tid":1266762,"uid":193209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b52ea717719ee3ef45b13604a358c54d3bef881","tid":1266762,"uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T1